ve%20to%20learn%20that%20skill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E9.%20You%20disrespect%20yourself.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22couple%20unhappy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef27aa96b7920019ca4c88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Efizkes%20%2F%20Shutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20had%20a%20past%20relationship%20that%20was%20difficult%2C%20abusive%2C%20or%20asymmetrical%20in%20some%20way%2C%20you%20may%20disrespect%20yourself%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20things%20your%20ex-partner%20said%2C%20according%20to%20Neo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tell%20ourselves%20things%20like%20'you're%20so%20stupid%2C'%20'how%20could%20you%20do%20this%20again%2C'%20and%20we%20scold%20ourselves%20all%20the%20time%20like%20this%20broken%20record%20in%20our%20heads%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20think%20carefully%20and%20think%20about%20whose%20voice%20is%20this%20really%2C%20you'll%20realize%20actually%20it's%20not%20your%20voice.%20You've%20just%20taken%20it%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20voice%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20you%20question%20and%20judge%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Neo%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20because%20of%20what%20he%20or%20she%20told%20you%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20it%20affects%20your%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20it%20is%20like%20the%20past%20keeping%20you%20in%20a%20box%2C%20she%20said.%20And%20part%20of%20breaking%20out%20of%20that%20box%20is%20realising%20your%20past%20relationship%20has%20no%20control%20over%20you%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E10.%20You%20re-live%20and%20re-create%20the%20past%20in%20your%20head.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22unhappy%20woman%20overthinking%2C%20lying%20in%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef282396b7920019ca4cd0%3Fforma