icult%20to%20not%20welcome%20the%20proposal%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections.%20The%20move%20will%20halve%20the%20presently%20crippling%20electioneering%20expenses%20for%20political%20parties.%20And%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20need%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20coming%20from%20clandestine%20and%20criminal%20sources%20ever%20since%20the%20ban%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20put%20on%20company%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20in%201970.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReunification%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20also%20make%20it%20far%20easier%20for%20a%20future%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20state%20financed%20and%20publicly%20audited%20system%20of%20election%20financing.%20This%20would%20not%20only%20weaken%20and%2C%20over%20time%2C%20eliminate%20the%20nexus%20between%20crime%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20also%20open%20the%20way%20for%20reforms%20in%20the%20police%20and%20lower%20administration%20that%20will%20cleanse%20the%20government%20of%20corruption%20and%20make%20it%20serve%20the%20people.%20It%20would%20also%20lengthen%20the%20time%20horizon%20over%20which%20government%20policies%20will%20need%20to%20bear%20fruit%3B%20restore%20the%20Centre-State%20co-ordination%20in%20policy%20making%20that%20was%20severely%20weakened%20by%20the%20separation%20of%20central%20from%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20facilitate%20structural%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felections-2024-india-most-dangerous-phase%5C%22%3EAs%20the%202024%20Elections%20Approach%2C%20India%20Is%20Entering%20the%20Most%20Dangerous%20Phase%20of%20Its%20Existence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20enacted%20with%20necessary%20safeguards%2C%20it%20will%20also%20put%20a%20brake%20on%20opportunistic%20defections%20from%20political%20parties.%20The%20most%20necessary%20of%20these%20safeguards%20will%20be%20an%20automatic%20declaration%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20till%20the%20next%20general%20election%20in%20any%20state%20where%20the%20government%20has%20been%20brought%20down%20by%20defections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reasons%20for%20taking%20this%20sudden%20decision%2C%20however%2C%20have%20little%20to%20do%20with%20better%20governance.%20He%20has%20taken%20it%20because%20he%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20BJP%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20suffering%20the%20same%20fate%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20possibly%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20that%20it%20suffered%20in%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20therefore%20understandably%20wary%20of%20going%20into%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20a%20string%20of%20electoral%20defeats%20in%20major%20states%20behind%20him.%20So%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%20%E2%80%93%20avoid%20four%20important%20state%20elections%20that%20his%20party%20could%20lose%2C%20and%20hold%20a%20combined%20national%20and%20state%20election%20with%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20G-20%20presidency%20and%20its%20grand%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20to%20buoy%20him%2C%20delivering%20both%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20to%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%2C%20Fourth%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20coalition%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20one-election%20proposal%20is%20therefore%20understandable.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20short-sighted%20because%20unifying%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20will%20resolve%20the%20most%20knotty%20problem%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20facing%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20next%20general%20election%20and%20greatly%20improve%20its%20chances%20of%20victory.%20This%20problem%20is%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20to%20its%20constituent%20parties%20in%20each%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20showed%2C%20the%20coalition%20is%20determined%20to%20field%20only%20one%20candidate%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20each%20constituency.%20But%20it%20has%20yet%20to%20decide%20from%20which%20party%2C%20and%20on%20what%20basis%20the%20candidate%20should%20be%20chosen.%20At%20the%20Patna%20meeting%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamta%20Bannerjee%20had%20told%20the%20press%20that%20the%20alliance%20would%20set%20up%20coordination%20committees%20that%20would%20first%20decide%20the%20principles%20they%20would%20follow%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20and%20then%20use%20these%20to%20choose%20the%20party%20and%20candidate%20for%20each%20constituency.%20Today%2C%20two%20more%20alliance%20meetings%20later%2C%20that%20process%20is%20only%20about%20to%20begin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20foot-dragging%20is%20taking%20place%20because%20the%20party%20leaders%20have%20not%20found%20a%20way%20to%20cross%20the%20main%20hurdle%20they%20face%3A%20how%20to%20retain%20the%20loyalty%20and%20support%20of%20their%20cadres%20in%20the%20constituencies%20that%20they%20have%20ceded%20to%20an%20ally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20problem%20would%20not%20have%20arisen%20if%20there%20had%20been%20a%20system%20of%20state%20financing%20of%20elections%20like%20the%20one%20Western%20Europe.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20parties%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20local%20financiers%20whom%20they%20offer%20government%20contracts%20and%20other%20favours%20if%20their%20party%20comes%20to%20power.%20This%20clientelist%20system%20starts%20breaking%20down%20if%20the%20financiers%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20party%2C%20or%20in%20its%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20win.%20It%20ceases%20to%20exist%20when%20the%20party%20has%20no%20horse%20in%20the%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20dilemma.%20This%20would%20confine%20the%20seat%20sharing%20between%20political%20parties%20only%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20allow%20full%20competition%20to%20continue%20between%20them%20sin%20the%20various%20state%20assemblies%20and%20also%20require%20them%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20demarcation%20between%20national%20and%20local%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParty%20cadres%20can%20then%20be%20instructed%20to%20emphasise%20national%20issues%20in%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20where%20their%20party%20is%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20and%20to%20place%20greater%20stress%20on%20state%20and%20local%20issues%20in%20those%20where%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20been%20allotted%20to%20another%20member%20of%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20dilemma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20student-loan%20borrowers%20could%20face%20a%20'perfect%20storm'%20of%20obstacles%20once%20payments%20resume%20next%20month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Class%20of%202020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0c37a5114270019ae6071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223126%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGraduation%20caps.%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Furlong%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20student-loan%20payment%20pause%20is%20officially%20over.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEven%20before%20it%20ended%2C%20borrowers%20were%20experiencing%20issues%20and%20mistakes%20with%20repayment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EExperts%20told%20Insider%20lack%20of%20broad%20debt%20relief%20and%20high%20inflation%20could%20contribute%20to%20the%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20student-loan%20payment%20pause%20is%20over%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20next%20chapter%20for%20borrowers%20won't%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%20three%20years%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20officially%20ended%20the%20pandemic%20pause%20on%20federal%20student-loan%20payments%2C%20with%20waived%20interest%2C%20on%20Friday.%20That%20means%20that%20millions%20of%20borrowers%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-will-interest-resume-federal-student-loan-debt-payment-pause-2023-7%5C%22%3Enow%20start%20seeing%20interest%20accumulate%20on%20their%20balances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%20October%2C%20their%20first%20payment%20required%20in%20years%20will%20come%20due.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20have%20already%20reported%20issues%20with%20repayment.%20One%20borrower%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-resume-confusion-borrowers-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20her%20student-loan%20company%20projected%20a%20%2449%2C000%20monthly%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20company%20admitted%20was%20a%20mistake%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she's%20still%20waiting%20for%20her%20statement%20to%20be%20corrected.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20it's%20been%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20borrowers%20to%20get%20ahold%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20manage%20their%20debt.%20One%20servicer%2C%20Nelnet%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-website-call-center-shut-down-borrowers-payments-2023-8%5C%22%3Ehas%20had%20to%20shut%20down%20its%20call%20center%20and%20website%20multiple%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20an%20influx%20of%20requests%20from%20borrowers%2C%20leaving%20many%20unable%20to%20access%20their%20accounts%20and%20determine%20their%20repayment%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolyn%20Fast%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20The%20Century%20Foundation%20who%20focuses%20on%20higher-education%20policy%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20some%20borrowers%20have%20never%20had%20to%20make%20payments%20on%20their%20loans%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic%20pause%2C%20and%20after%20three%20years%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20big%20job%26quot%3B%20in%20facilitating%20this%20transition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20confusion%20and%20questions%20that%20borrowers%20have%20about%20what%20their%20obligations%20and%20options%20are%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Fast%20said.%20%26quot%3BMany%20are%20worried%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20perfect%20storm%20of%20bureaucratic%20obstacles%20for%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20obstacles%20will%20likely%20include%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20and%20funding%20for%20the%20Education%20Department%2C%20paperwork%20issues%20for%20borrowers%2C%20and%20inflation%20that%20could%20strain%20borrowers'%20budgets%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20foot%20another%20monthly%20bill.%20An%20Education%20Department%20spokesperson%20recently%20told%20Insider%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20regularly%20communicate%20with%20borrowers%20and%20share%20repayment%20options%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-student-loan-repayment-plan-debt-relief-repayment-save-idr-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20new%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20intended%20to%20make%20payments%20more%20affordable.%20The%20agency%20also%20said%20it%20remains%20in%20frequent%20contact%20with%20servicers%20to%20ensure%20they%20directly%20communicate%20repayment%20information%20to%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20trying%20to%20do%20whatever%20they%20can%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20runs%20smoothly%2C%26quot%3B%20Fast%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20still%20going%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20challenge%20for%20the%20department.%26quot%3B%20Here%20are%20the%20challenges%20borrowers%20could%20encounter%20as%20they%20begin%20to%20make%20payments%20again%20this%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'This%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20shock%20to%20their%20budgets'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Biden%20intended%20for%20borrowers%20to%20restart%20payments%20with%20a%20reduction%20to%20their%20balances%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20June%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20his%20plan%20to%20cancel%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20federal%20student%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stephanie%20Hall%2C%20the%20acting%20senior%20director%20of%20higher%20education%20policy%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20Biden's%20debt-relief%20plan%20%26quot%3Bwould%20have%20actually%20cleared%20out%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20borrowers%20from%20the%2