ents%20in%20a%20classroom%20slap%20a%20Muslim%20boy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20failing%20to%20memorise%20the%20multiplication%20table%20of%20five.%20The%20older%20excuse%20to%20punish%20a%20child%20for%20not%20learning%20his%20lessons%20becomes%20an%20excuse%20(even%20alibi)%20to%20institute%20the%20principle%20of%20an%20un-secular%20punishment.%20As%20the%20boy%20was%20being%20hit%2C%20the%20teacher%20nonchalantly%20spoke%20about%20Muslim%20students%20in%20pejorative%20terms%2C%20marking%20out%20a%20community.%20When%20the%20teacher%20noticed%20some%20students%20were%20not%20executing%20her%20order%20ruthlessly%2C%20not%20hitting%20the%20boy%20hard%20enough%2C%20she%20urged%20them%20to%20slap%20harder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20brutal%20theatre%20was%20captured%20on%20mobile%20camera%20by%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20cousin%20who%20was%20there%20by%20chance.%20He%20was%20an%20accidental%20witness%20to%20the%20agonising%20scene%2C%20showing%20remarkable%20poise%20to%20balance%20his%20feelings%20on%20his%20hands.%20His%20camera%20gives%20us%20an%20idea%20how%20the%20teacher%20was%20introducing%20a%20fascistic%20sport%20to%20children%20in%20a%20classroom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20act%20broke%20the%20normative%20codes%20of%20punishment%20imparted%20in%20schools.%20We%20trust%20schoolteachers%20and%20agree%20on%20their%20authority%20as%20part%20of%20a%20contract%2C%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20lies%20in%20our%20modern%20social%20imaginary%3A%20teachers%20are%20expected%20to%20follow%20secular%20and%20egalitarian%20principles%2C%20treat%20students%20equally%2C%20and%20without%20prejudice.%20This%20code%20is%20of%20course%20never%20strictly%20followed.%20Students%20who%20are%20not%20considered%20bright%2C%20or%20who%20come%20from%20economically%20poor%20backgrounds%2C%20are%20often%20ignored%2C%20or%20treated%20badly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20teacher%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20unleashed%20two%20disturbing%20psycho-social%20consequences%20at%20the%20same%20time%3A%20she%20made%20the%20Muslim%20boy%20feel%20his%20self-respect%20is%20in%20jeopardy%20because%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewho%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20he%20is.%20His%20being%20Muslim%20was%20enough%20provocation%20for%20others%20to%20rob%20him%20off%20his%20sovereignty%2C%20his%20pride%20and%20his%20wellbeing.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20teacher%20made%20other%20students%20feel%20triumphant%20about%20their%20social%20identity%20and%20encouraged%20them%20to%20collectively%20humiliate%20the%20student%20who%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20their%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20students%20who%20were%20ordered%20to%20slap%20the%20Muslim%20boy%20had%20no%20institutional%20or%20moral%20right%20to%20do%20so.%20Yet%2C%20the%20teacher%20empowered%20them%20to%20turn%20into%20punishers%20in%20the%20classroom.%20Their%20reluctance%20to%20hit%20the%20boy%20hard%20was%20proof%20of%20their%20conscience.%20The%20teacher%20wanted%20them%20to%20lose%20their%20ethical%20hesitancy%20in%20order%20to%20fulfil%20her%20perverse%20wish%20of%20singling%20out%20someone%20from%20a%20minority%20community%20for%20harsh%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20this%2C%20being%20a%20student%20took%20a%20back%20seat.%20In%20that%20inhumane%20hour%2C%20the%20children%20in%20the%20classroom%20were%20made%20to%20forget%20their%20primary%20identity%20of%20being%20students.%20They%20were%20divided%20along%20religious%20lines%20by%20a%20devious%20command%20that%20separated%20their%20worth%20and%20power%20according%20to%20their%20communal%20identity.%20The%20classroom%20was%20transformed%20into%20an%20amphitheatre%20of%20communal%20vigilantism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20act%20will%20have%20ironic%20and%20unintended%20consequences.%20The%20scars%20of%20the%20incident%20that%20violated%20his%20presence%20in%20the%20world%20will%20haunt%20the%20Muslim%20boy%20at%20least%20for%20some%20time.%20It%20is%20through%20incidents%20like%20these%20that%20vulnerable%20people%20experience%20the%20real%20test%2C%20and%20limits%2C%20of%20being%20human.%20The%20boy%20is%20made%20to%20realise%20the%20pain%20of%20being%20human%20through%20the%20lack%2C%20or%20loss%2C%20of%20the%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20humanity%20that%20leads%20her%20to%20practise%20humiliation.%20Dehumanisation%20provokes%2C%20but%20also%2C%20paradoxically%2C%20restores%20our%20shocked%20humanity.%20Being%20human%20is%20never%20easy%2C%20often%20realised%20through%20painful%20experiences.%20A%20sense%20of%20humanity%20is%20realised%20in%20such%20grim%20moments%20of%20awareness%20when%20you%20face%20the%20inhumane.%20Socially%20administered%20victimhood%20is%20the%20most%20acute%20condition%20that%20marks%20the%20relational%20predicaments%20of%20being%20human.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20teacher%20also%20failed%20to%20anticipate%20is%20that%20her%20favoured%20children%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ones%20she%20used%20as%20little%20pawns%20for%20her%20hate-game%20%E2%80%93%20may%20end%20up%20losing%20their%20human%20sensibility%20if%20they%20take%20her%20game%20seriously.%20She%20was%20damaging%20the%20children%20she%20was%20empowering.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECollective%20hate%20corrodes%20the%20conscience%20of%20each%20individual%20who%20participates%20in%20it.%20If%20young%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20gang%20up%20against%20fellow%20students%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religious%20difference%2C%20they%20will%20soon%20feel%20they%20are%20above%20the%20moral%20law%20that%20runs%20a%20secular%20institution.%20They%20may%20get%20tempted%20to%20take%20this%20game%20into%20the%20streets.%20The%20feeling%20of%20being%20a%20powerful%20herd%20can%20inspire%20them%20to%20also%20one%20day%20topple%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20teacher.%20That%20day%20the%20moral%20breakdown%20of%20an%20institution%20and%20a%20society%20will%20be%20complete.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EManash%20Firaq%20Bhattacharjee%20is%20an%20author.%20His%20latest%20book%20is%3C%2Fem%3E%20Nehru%20and%20the%20Spirit%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693821248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04152208%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.21.24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fmuzaffarnagar-slapping-teacher-punishment-muslim%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teacher%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20was%20damaging%20the%20very%20children%20she%20was%20empowering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fmuzaffarnagar-slapping-teacher-punishment-muslim%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asia%20Cup%20Live%3A%20Ishan%20Kishan%20Drops%20Sitter%2C%20India%20Sloppy%20In%20Field%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20vs%20Nepal%2C%20Asia%20Cup%202023%2C%20Live%20Updates%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA