2ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-says-chandrayaan-3-lander-vikram-set-into-sleep-mode-on-moon-hoping-for-their-awakening-around-september-22-4357742%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20worked%20alongside%20former%20US%20President%20Jimmy%20Carter%20for%2030%20years.%20Here's%20what%20he's%20been%20like%20as%20a%20mentor.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221255%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karin%20Ryan%20and%20Jimmy%20Carter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f48d0f781926001910a91a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22941%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BJimmy%20Carter%20has%20the%20soul%20of%20an%20activist%20and%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20pragmatist%2C%26quot%3B%20writes%20Karin%20Ryan%2C%20shown%20with%20the%20former%20US%20president.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Karin%20Ryan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKarin%20Ryan%20has%20worked%20alongside%20former%20US%20President%20Jimmy%20Carter%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe's%20been%20most%20touched%20by%20his%20faith%20in%20the%20goodness%20of%20others%20and%20his%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20peace.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20has%20high%20expectations%20and%20has%20always%20been%20more%20demanding%20of%20those%20closest%20to%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20more%20than%2030%20years%20of%20working%20with%20former%20US%20President%20Jimmy%20Carter%2C%20I've%20been%20most%20touched%20by%20his%20deep%20faith%20in%20people%20%E2%80%94%20his%20belief%20that%2C%20given%20the%20chance%2C%20everyone%20has%20the%20capacity%20for%20good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20always%20been%20confident%20that%20even%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20and%20persecuted%20can%20rise%20above%20any%20challenge%20if%20they%20have%20adequate%20resources%20and%20support%2C%20and%20he%20built%20The%20Carter%20Center%20to%20help%20fill%20this%20need.%20He's%20approached%20the%20powerful%20%E2%80%94%20be%20they%20warlords%20or%20heads%20of%20state%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0with%20a%20presumption%20that%20an%20appeal%20to%20reason%2C%20communicated%20with%20respect%2C%20might%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20sometimes%20heard%20him%20called%20na%C3%AFve.%20This%20is%20wrong%3A%20His%20beliefs%20and%20actions%20have%20always%20been%20well%20informed.%20It's%20with%20eyes%20wide%20open%20that%20he%20chooses%20optimism%2C%20possibility%2C%20and%20faith%20over%20cynicism%20and%20arrogance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20constant%20inspiration%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20something%20life-changing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20drawn%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cartercenter.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Carter%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20moving%20to%20Atlanta%20in%201987.%20During%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20Center's%20museum%2C%20I%20was%20captivated%20by%20exhibits%20showcasing%20the%20Camp%20David%20peace%20talks%20and%20the%20success%20of%20Carter's%20Panama%20Canal%20Treaty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEncountering%20the%20determination%20of%20this%20American%20president%20who%20was%20so%20deeply%20devoted%20to%20peace%20was%20a%20life-changing%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20an%20entry-level%20position%20in%20the%20newly%20established%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cartercenter.org%2Fpeace%2Fhuman_rights%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman%20Rights%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%20opened%20up%20at%20the%20Center%2C%20I%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20apply.%20I%20organized%20meetings%2C%20took%20phone%20messages%20(this%20was%20before%20voicemail!)%2C%20and%20eventually%20got%20to%20help%20research%20cases%20of%20political%20prisoners%20and%20draft%20letters%20for%20Carter%20on%20their%20behalf.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarter%20liked%20to%20work%20through%20memos%20instead%20of%20frequent%20meetings%20so%20we%20had%20to%20present%20our%20ideas%20in%20brief%20paragraphs%20and%20learn%20to%20draft%20letters%20that%20he%20might%20have%20written%20as%20president%20%E2%80%94%20short%20and%20to%20the%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20cannot%20count%20how%20many%20drafts%20came%20back%20from%20him%20with%20notes%20in%20the%20margin%20saying%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Btoo%20verbose%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20Amnesty%20International!%26quot%3B%20He%20didn't%20want%20strident%20activist%20language%20in%20his%20letters%3B%20moral%20persuasion%20from%20a%20former%20President%20required%20something%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Jimmy%20Carter%20and%20Karin%20Ryan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f490cf1b7ced0019c7896b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Jimmy%20Carter%20and%20Karin%20Ryan%20shown%20during%20a%201990%20Carter-Menil%20Human%20Rights%20Prize%20selection%20committee%20meeting.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Karin%20Ryan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20appreciated%20my%20focus%20on%20human%20rights%20activists%20as%20key%20agents%20of%20democratic%20movements%20and%20began%20to%20ask%20me%20for%20input%20during%20his%20various%20forays%20into%20diplomacy.%20Once%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20the%20team%20that%20would%20observe%20the%20first%20democratic%20elections%20in%20Haiti%20in%201990%20so%20that%20I%20could%20find%20leading%20dissident%20voices%20and%20journalists%20with%20whom%20he%20could%20meet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discussions%20he%20had%20on%20that%20trip%20were%20deep%20and%20intense%2C%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20usual%20predictable%20official%20meetings.%20At%20the%20conclusion%20of%20our%20stay%20in%20Haiti%2C%20Carter%20turned%20to%20me%20before%20stepping%20into%20his%20ride%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BYou%20did%20a%20good%20job%20here.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBelief%20in%20the%20inherent%20goodness%20of%20others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20became%20a%20model%20for%20our%20future%20work%20together%3A%20The%20Carter%20Center%20has%20continued%20to%20bring%20together%20frontline%20activists%20for%20those%20tough%20but%20transformative%20conversations%20%E2%80%94%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20advancing%20human%20rights%20and%20democracy%20in%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarter's%20belief%20in%20the%20inherent%20goodness%20of%20people%20has%20never%20faded%2C%20despite%20the%20grave%20disappointments%20and%20turmoil%20of%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Iraq%20invasion%2C%20America's%20abuses%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20terror%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20global%20erosion%20of%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20his%20faith%20in%20humanity%20%E2%80%94%20the%20root%20of%20his%20commitment%20to%20human%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20has%20seemed%20to%20grow%20stronger%20as%20he's%20aged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20decades%20at%20The%20Carter%20Center%2C%20he's%20written%20countless%20letters%20on%20behalf%20of%20victims%20of%20abuse%2C%20especially%20human%20rights%20activists%20persecuted%20for%20their%20brave%20work.%20A%20letter%20he%20wrote%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Nepal%20resulted%20in%20hundreds%20of%20people%20being%20released%20from%20prison.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Carter%20once%20dropped%20into%20my%20office%20asking%20why%20I%20hadn't%20sent%20him%20any%20cases%20recently.%20He%20wanted%20to%20use%20his%20voice%20and%20his%20name%20to%20help%20people%20in%20trouble.%20He%20often%20kept%20his%20personal%20interventions%20on%20behalf%20of%20political%20prisoners%20private%2C%20because%20he%20believed%20that%20would%20make%20them%20more%20effective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20criticize%20foreign%20governments%2C%20he%20has%20been%20sometimes%20even%20more%20critical%20of%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20his%20own%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Rosalynn%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20often%20intimately%20involved%20in%20his%20peacemaking%20and%20human%20rights%20efforts%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20wrote%20many%20letters%20on%20behalf%20of%20Americans%20facing%20execution%2C%20rarely%20successfully.%20He%20has%20also%20made%20public%20appeals%20to%20governors%20to%20abolish%20the%20death%20penalty%20in%20their%20states%2C%20sometimes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeathpenaltyinfo.org%2Fnews%2Fnew-voices-jimmy-carter-former-president-and-nobel-peace-prize-winner-calls-for-end-to-death-penalty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccessfully%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20issued%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2003%2F03%2F09%2Fopinion%2Fjust-war-or-a-just-war.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escathing%20condemnations%20of%20the%202003%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2012%2F06%2F25%2Fopinion%2Famericas-shameful-human-rights-record.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuman%20rights%20violations%20by%20the%20US%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20end%20or%20avoid%20war%20sometimes%20meant%20that%20he%20would%20not%20speak%20publicly%20about%20human%20rights%20abuses%20committed%20by%20warring%20parties%2C%20seeking%20instead%20an%20end%20to%20the%20violence%20first.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20peacemaking%20efforts%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fwgbh%2Fpages%2Ffrontline%2Fshows%2Fkim%2Finterviews%2Fcarter.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20North%20Korea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Farchive%2Fpolitics%2F1994%2F12%2F21%2Fcarter-gets-bosnian-foes-to-agree-to-a-cease-fire%2Fb51ed360-4c88-482e-8f02-d71b94f01dbd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Bosnia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1994%2F09%2F19%2Fworld%2Fshowdown-in-haiti-carter-carter-s-diplomatic-mission-was-a-last-minute-gamble.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Haiti%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201994%2C%20we%20organized%20a%20closed-door%20discussion%20with%20U.S.-based%20human%20rights%20leaders%20critical%20of%20his%20engagements%20with%20human%20rights%20violators.%20During%20the%20contentious%20discussion%2C%20the%20Carters%20made%20their%20case%20for%20avoiding%20withholding%20public%20condemnations%20that%20could%20derail%20efforts%20to%20bring%20leaders%20like%20Kim%20Il%20Sung%2C%20Radovan%20Karadzic%2C%20and%20Raoul%20C%C3%A9dras%20to%20the%20peace%20table.%20Ultimately%2C%20he%20agreed%20that%20the%20peace%20process%20should%20never%20preclude%20holding%20human%20rights%20violators%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20vocal%20supporter%20of%20U.N.%20negotiations%20to%20establish%20an%20independent%20International%20Criminal%20Court%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cartercenter.org%2Fnews%2Fdocuments%2Fdoc1377.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20publicly%20opposing%20a%20U.S.%20proposal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20give%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20a%20veto%20over%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20independent%20chief%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoul%20of%20an%20activist%2C%20mind%20of%20a%20pragmatist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20Carter%20has%20the%20soul%20of%20an%20activist%20and%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20pragmatist.%20Every%20situation%20has%20required%20a%20balancing%20of%20objectives%2C%20though%20his%20calculations%20were%20always%20informed%20by%20his%20ideas%20about%20the%20value%20of%20human%20freedom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20remarkable%20thing%20to%20witness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20be%20so%20positive%20and%20encouraging%20one%20moment%2C%20and%20stern%20and%20insistent%20the%20next.%20In%202009%2C%20the%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Committee%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Knesset%20peppered%20Carter%20with%20questions%2C%20suggesting%20he%20supported%20Hamas%20because%20he%20met%20with%20their%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20gently%20but%20firmly%20pushed%20back%2C%20reminding%20committee%20members%20that%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Ariel%20Sharon%20had%20personally%20approved%20of%20Hamas%20candidates%20running%20in%20the%202006%20elections.%20His%20focus%20was%20simple%3A%20peace%20and%20human%20rights%20for%20all%2C%20which%20requires%20speaking%20with%20all%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Cold%20War%20president%2C%20Carter%20walked%20a%20tightrope%20of%20managing%20relationships%20with%20world%20leaders%20while%20speaking%20out%20against%20human%20rights%20abuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20he%20navigated%20a%20nuclear-arms%20reduction%20while%20standing%20with%20dissidents%2C%20sending%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1977%2F02%2F18%2Farchives%2Fsakharov-receives-carter-letter-affirming-commitment-on-rights.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20hand-written%3C%2Fa%3E%20letter%20of%20support%20to%20embattled%20physicist%20Andrei%20Sakharov.%20He%20threatened%20Latin%20American%20Soviet%20allies%20like%20Argentina%20with%20an%20end%20to%20military%20assistance%20if%20they%20persisted%20with%20human%20rights%20abuses%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20that%20bolstered%20democratic%20movements%20across%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20China%2C%20he%20pressured%20the%20government%20to%20allow%20a%20measure%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalministries.org%2Fjimmy_carter_bible_10_10_2014_1257%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20religious%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shine.cn%2Fnews%2Fnation%2F1911226652%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20student%20exchanges%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20political%20prisoner%20releases.%20And%20while%20he%20has%20succeeded%20in%20forging%20a%20lasting%20peace%20between%20Israel%20and%20Egypt%2C%20he%20has%20also%20dedicated%20himself%20and%20The%20Carter%20Center%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20equal%20human%20rights%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20the%20unfinished%20business%20of%20the%20Camp%20David%20Accords.%20When%20quiet%20diplomacy%20failed%20to%20achieve%20this%20aim%2C%20he%20became%20increasingly%20critical%20of%20both%20Israeli%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20U.S.%20to%20exert%20its%20influence%20to%20stop%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJimmy%20Carter%20is%20a%20mentor%20that's%20most%20demanding%20of%20those%20closest%20to%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20greatest%20hope%20for%20his%20own%20country%20is%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20United%20States%20will%20realize%20that%20our%20great%20blessings%20could%20allow%20us%20to%20be%20a%20generous%2C%20justice-oriented%2C%20and%20peace-loving%20nation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karin%20Ryan%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f49123781926001910aa0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKarin%20Ryan%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Karin%20Ryan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20never%20had%20the%20feeling%20that%20this%20was%20just%20wishful%20thinking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20faith.%20Many%20of%20us%20who%20know%20him%20and%20have%20worked%20by%20his%20side%20are%20dee