of%20well-paying%20jobs%20relative%20to%20the%20size%20of%20our%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20lucrative%20jobs%20have%20not%20only%20elevated%20Midland's%20population%20and%20homeownership%20rate%2C%20but%20have%20also%20spurred%20a%20demand%20for%20additional%20businesses%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20city's%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20young%20millennials%20that%20own%20homes%20are%20also%20raising%20families%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20mayor%2C%20it's%20a%20huge%20priority%20to%20find%20family-friendly%20opportunities%20for%20economic%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20due%20to%20a%20significant%20segment%20of%20Midland's%20population%20working%20in%20the%20oil%20and%20energy%20sector%2C%20the%20city%20has%20shortfalls%20in%20employment%20across%20other%20sectors%20such%20as%20banking%2C%20hospitality%2C%20and%20entertainment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlong%20said%20one%20of%20her%20objectives%20as%20mayor%20is%20to%20boost%20the%20city's%20workforce.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20have%20enough%20people%20to%20do%20all%20the%20jobs%20that%20are%20needed%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%C2%A0%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20in%20an%20oil%20field%2C%20or%20in%20retail%2C%20food%2C%20and%20beverage%20service%2C%20we%20have%20a%20great%20need%20for%20more%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAriel%20Herrera%2C%2027%2C%20cofounder%20and%20co-owner%20of%20The%20Tailgate%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223635%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ariel%20Herrera%2C%20the%20co-owner%20and%20founder%20of%20The%20Tailgate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f208d75114270019af4d57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAriel%20Herrera%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20co-owner%20of%20The%20Tailgate.%3Cp%3EAlcynna%20Lloyd%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAriel%20Herrera%2C%20a%20former%20Austin%20resident%2C%20came%20to%20Midland%2