0born%20and%20raised%20in%20Midland.%20He%20has%20witnessed%20the%20city's%20evolution%20from%20a%20well-known%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fleerebs.com%2Fschool-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-school%20football%20hub%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20current%20status%20as%20a%20popular%20destination%20for%20millennials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20that%20Midland's%20boom%20in%20young%20residents%20has%20ushered%20in%20more%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20city%20is%20totally%20different%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20especially%20for%20someone%20like%20my%20dad%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendrick%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BHe%20went%20to%20school%20in%20Midland%20when%20it%20was%20still%20segregated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20days%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20people%20and%20diversity%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20real-estate%20agent%2C%20Kendrick%20has%20also%20observed%20the%20impact%20millennials%20have%20had%20on%20the%20real%20estate%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20segment%20of%20my%20clients%20are%20millennials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20either%20just%20got%20married%2C%20or%20they're%20about%20to%20have%20kids%2C%20or%20they're%20selling%20their%20first%20home%20to%20purchase%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kendrick%2C%20the%20abundance%20of%20millennial%20homebuyers%20has%20led%20to%20an%20imbalance%20of%20supply%20and%20demand%20in%20Midland%2C%20which%20has%20reduced%20housing%20affordability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202021%2C%20the%20median%20listing%20price%20in%20Midland%20was%20just%20%24329%2C000%2C%20however%20in%202023%2C%20that%20price%20has%20jumped%20to%20%24388%2C500%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Realtor.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMidland%20is%20experiencing%20a%20housing%20shortage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSix%20months'%20supply%20is%20considered%20normal%20for%20inventory%20and%20we%20haven't%20had%20more%20than%20three%20months%20of%20supply%20since%20I%20became%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20in%202015.%20It's%20led%20to%20prices%20consistently%20rising%20in%20the%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChristine%20Foreman%2C%2050%2C%20public%20liaison%20with%20Region%2018%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christine%20Foreman%2C%2050%2C%20public%20liaison%20with%20Region%2018%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f208c65114270019af4d33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristine%20Foreman%20in%20downtown%20Midland.%3Cp%3EAlcynna%20Lloyd%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChristine%20Foreman%20has%20lived%20in%20Midland%20her%20entire%20life.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20of%20three%20works%20as%20a%20public%20liaison%20with%20Region%2018%2C%20an%20education%20service%20center%20that%20assists%20Texas%20school%20districts%20in%20improving%20student%20performance.%20She%20also%20serves%20on%20several%20educational%20boards%2C%20and%20is%20a%20longtime%20volunteer%20with%20the%20Parents%20and%20Teachers%20Association.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeman%20told%20me%20that%20Midland's%20ongoing%20expansion%20has%20created%20more%20problems%20for%20its%20public%20schools.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20campuses%20are%20deteriorating%2C%20classrooms%20are%20full%20to%20capacity%2C%20and%20students%20lack%20fundamental%20resources%20such%20as%20access%20to%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Foreman%20pulled%20her%20own%20daughter%20out%20of%20Midland%20High%20School.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20her%20school's%20classrooms%20had%20zero%20connectivity%20to%20the%20internet%2C''%20Foreman%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BShe%20would%20waste%20an%20hour%20in%20a%20classroom%20not%20being%20able%20to%20do%20schoolwork%2C%20so%20we%20just%20let%20her%20stay%20virtual%20for%20the%20re