6IjFtY3I3cUdYbVVpMG1Lb2tpdnk5SkE9PSIsInZhbHVlIjoiNFZ1Wlp0Mmphb2xpVmpvckVxZk1mdz09IiwibWFjIjoiZTdmZjllYjQ2NmJiNGQyZjM3ZmY1YmIxY2ZiYWQwMWE5MTJlOTljYTI3ZDc1NGIwN2YyNDJjMTBmNmExOTJlNiJ9%5C%22%3EAs%20on%20April%2028%2C%202023%2C%20around%20Rs%2012%2C008.5%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20appraised%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20project%2C%20of%20which%20only%20Rs%204%2C923%20crore%20has%20been%20released%20and%20Rs%202%2C521%20crore%20has%20been%20utilised%20(which%20is%20roughly%20around%2021%25%20of%20the%20appraised%20amount%20and%2051%25%20of%20the%20released%20amount).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20spent%20Rs%20160%20crore%20on%20another%20important%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fschemes%2Fone-stop-centre-scheme-1%5C%22%3EOne%20Stop%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202020-21.%20The%20scheme%2C%20initially%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Mission%20for%20Protection%20and%20Empowerment%20for%20Women%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20now%20subsumed%2C%20with%20many%20other%20pre-existing%20and%20new%20schemes%2C%20under%20a%20new%20programme%2C%20%E2%80%98Sambal%E2%80%99%20of%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Shakti%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20no%20longer%20is%20possible%20to%20find%20out%20how%20much%20was%20allocated%20for%20the%20scheme%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Sambal%E2%80%99%20subsumes%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98One%20Stop%20Centre%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENari%20Adalat%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98Mahila%20Police%20Volunteer%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98Women%E2%80%99s%20Helpline%E2%80%99.%20Of%20the%20total%20allocated%20amount%20of%20Rs%20587%20crore%20for%20Sambal%20in%202021-22%2C%20Rs%20183%20crore%2C%20or%20roughly%20around%2031%25%2C%20has%20been%20used%20in%20that%20particular%20year.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20allocation%20for%20the%20scheme%20was%20reduced%20to%20Rs%20562%20crore%20in%20subsequent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3