ers%20is%20to%20preselect%20your%20replacement%20items%20and%20always%20tip%20fairly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Ashley%20Colon%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20Instacart%20shopper%20from%20Ridgefield%20Park%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20earnings%20with%20documentation.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20loved%20side%20hustles.%20Even%20though%20I%20work%20full%20time%20as%20a%20public-relations%20account%20coordinator%2C%20whenever%20I%20have%20a%20free%20evening%20or%20weekend%2C%20I%20look%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-side-hustles-perfect-for-summer-months-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20way%20to%20make%20more%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20started%20my%20own%20business%20selling%20chocolate-covered%20strawberries%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20a%20babysitter.%20After%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-files-prospectus-with-sec-ahead-of-ipo-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstacart%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20work%20to%20send%20products%20to%20reporters%20from%20the%20food%20and%20beverage%20brands%20my%20company%20represents%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20test%20out%20working%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20to%20work%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shopper-works-18-hour-days-road-trips-cities-orders-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstacart%20as%20a%20shopper%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March.%20While%20the%20only%20qualifications%20you%20need%20are%20a%20driver's%20license%2C%20a%20vehicle%2C%20and%20a%20background%20check%20that%20comes%20back%20good%2C%20it%20still%20took%20me%20four%20weeks%20to%20get%20accepted%20because%20in%20my%20town%2C%20there%20was%20a%20waiting%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20as%20a%20shopper%2C%20I%20make%20between%20%24150%20and%20%24200%20on%20an%20average%20weekend%20day%20where%20I%20work%20eight%20to%2010%20hours.%20This%20includes%20tips%2C%20which%20average%20for%20me%20between%20%245%20and%20%2415.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstacart%20shopping%20is%20flexible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20any%20minimum%20work%20obligations.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20I%20have%20the%20time%2C%20I'll%20log%20on%20to%20the%20app%20and%20accept%20customer%20shopping%20requests.%20What%20I%20make%20varies%20based%20on%20how%20many%20orders%20I%20accept%2C%20how%20large%20the%20orders%20are%2C%20and%20how%20much%20the%20customer%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20customer%20gets%20to%20choose%20which%20store%20they%20would%20like%20to%20order%20from.%20I%20tend%20to%20choose%20orders%20based%20on%20distance%2C%20total%20pay%2C%20number%20of%20items%2C%20and%20my%20familiarity%20with%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enjoy%20shopping%20for%20customers%2C%20but%20the%20work%20can%20be%20stressful%20because%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20mess%20up%20someone's%20order.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20detail-oriented%20and%20not%20rush%20the%20shopping%20so%20I%20limit%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20my%20grocery%20trips%20are%20standard%2C%20I%20once%20had%20a%20customer%20ask%20me%20to%20deliver%2080%20cucumbers%20to%20their%20house.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20they%20made%20a%20mistake%20but%20they%20didn't%2C%20and%20I%20delivered%2080%20cucumbers%20to%20a%20very%20satisfied%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20made%20almost%20%24800%20in%20April%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20worked%20weekdays%2C%20too%2C%20after%20my%20full-time%20job%2C%20and%20I%20usually%20don't%20do%20that.%20Instacart%20doesn't%20offer%20an%20hourly%20rate%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20standard%20batch%20rate%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20distance%20and%20the%20number%20of%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20very%20small%20orders%20that%20are%20close%20by%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-say-they-cant-keep-working-after-pay-cut-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20batch%20rate%20starts%20at%20%244%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20goes%20up%20to%20over%20%2410.%20Another%20factor%20is%20an%20item's%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20heavy%20items%2C%20such%20as%20multiple%20cases%20of%20water%20bump%20up%20the%20batch%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20as%20an%20Instacart%20shopper%20for%20five%20months%20and%20having%20completed%20over%20100%20orders%2C%20I%20have%20some%20tips%20for%20people%20to%20know%20before%20they%20use%20a%20grocery-delivery%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Select%20replacement%20items%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20easy%20way%20to%20receive%20your%20order%20faster%20and%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20satisfied%20is%20to%20preselect%20replacements.%20That%20way%2C%20if%20what%20you%20originally%20wanted%20isn't%20in%20stock%2C%20your%20shopper%20knows%20what%20to%20grab%20for%20you%20instead%20without%20having%20to%20wait%20for%20your%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20preselect%20that%20you%20want%20the%20shopper%20to%20find%20a%20replacement%2C%20you%20may%20end%20up%20not%20being%20happy%20with%20what%20they%20pick%20up%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20time%20picking%20out%20replacement%20items%2C%20just%20select%20the%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20replace%26quot%3B%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Order%20ahead%20to%20save%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20easy%20way%20to%20save%20money%20is%20to%20order%20your%20groceries%20ahead%20of%20time.%20The%20Instacart%20app%20offers%20a%20%242%20discount%20when%20you%20select%20a%20three-hour%20delivery%20window%20or%20schedule%20grocery%20delivery%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20This%20doesn't%20affect%20the%20shoppers%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20a%20benefit%20to%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20need%20to%20rush%20your%20groceries%20or%20get%20an%20item%20delivered%20to%20you%20fast%2C%20this%20isn't%20the%20best%20option%2C%20but%20it%20could%20benefit%20those%20who%20use%20the%20app%20on%20a%20weekly%20basis%20for%20their%20standard%20grocery%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Give%20clear%20instructions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECommunication%20is%20crucial%20when%20you're%20using%20a%20grocery-delivery%20service.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20tell%20your%20shopper%20to%20leave%20your%20groceries%20at%20the%20door%2C%20they%20may%20not%20know%20which%20one%20%E2%80%94%20some%20people%20have%20front%2C%20side%2C%20and%20back%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20notice%20there%20are%20multiple%20doors%20and%20no%20clear%20instructions%2C%20I'll%20try%20to%20chat%20with%20the%20customer%20and%20ask%20them.%20If%20they%20don't%20get%20back%20to%20me%2C%20I%20put%20the%20groceries%20somewhere%20that's%20out%20of%20the%20sun%20and%20not%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20possible%2C%20keep%20your%20phone%20on%20you%20when%20your%20shopper%20is%20working%20on%20your%20order.%20They%20may%20even%20reach%20out%20to%20ask%20whether%20you%20have%20specific%20preferences%20for%20items%2C%20such%20as%20unripe%20bananas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20spot%20something%20that%20looks%20like%20an%20error%2C%20I%20like%20to%20confirm%20it.%20I%20once%20had%20someone%20order%205%20pounds%20of%20bananas.%20When%20I%20asked%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%2C%20they%20said%20they%20actually%20wanted%20only%20five%20bananas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Tip%20your%20shopper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20think%20I'm%20just%20picking%20up%20their%20order%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-say-long-drives-200-item-orders-becoming-common-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebut%20it's%20more%20intense%20than%20that%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20the%20person%20in%20the%20store%20grabbing%20everything%20you%20need%20and%20then%20lugging%20it%20into%20my%20car%20to%20drop%20it%20off%20at%20your%20house.%20I%20also%20carry%20people's%20orders%20up%20flights%20of%20stairs%20(if%20there%20isn't%20an%20elevator)%20or%20to%20their%20back%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20lets%20shoppers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-wait-in-parking-lots-to-claim-orders-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoose%20which%20orders%20they%20want%20to%20take%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20can%20see%20in%20advance%20whether%20a%20person%20has%20decided%20to%20tip%20a%20shopper.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20shoppers%20who%20won't%20accept%20orders%20where%20there's%20not%20a%20tip%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lowest%20recommended%20tip%20is%205%25%20of%20your%20order%20price%2C%20but%20customers%20should%20set%20a%20base%20tip.%20Instead%20of%20doing%205%25%2C%20it's%20much%20more%20beneficial%20to%20shoppers%20to%20set%20a%20number%20such%20as%20%245%20or%20%2410%20because%20if%20a%20shopper%20has%20to%20refund%20an%20item%20from%20your%20order%20because%20it's%20out%20of%20stock%2C%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20the%20order%20is%20reduced%2C%20so%20the%20tip%20is%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20getting%20tipped%20fairly%20and%20working%20effectively%2C%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20earn%20extra%20cash%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shopper-tips-better-cheaper-grocery-delivery-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693818601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0de4457bff7001947d022%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shopper-tips-better-cheaper-grocery-delivery-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Instacart%20shopper%20Ashley%20Colon%20says%20customers%20can%20have%20a%20bette