20of%20all)%20model.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20African%20Union%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20whether%20joining%20the%20G20%20would%20be%20beneficial%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fafrican-union-likely-tobecome-21st-member-of-g20-2611449.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%E2%80%9CAfrica%20is%20a%20large%20continent%20and%20the%20challenges%2C%20economy%20and%20communities%20are%20very%20diverse.%20In%20that%20context%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20this%20inclusion%20in%20the%20G20%20would%20not%20translate%20into%20anything%20for%20us%20in%20the%20literal%20sense.%20The%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20must%20be%20heard%20but%20the%20inclusion%20in%20G20%20would%20not%20help%20in%20addressing%20the%20concerns.%20We%20are%20grateful%20for%20India%20to%20consider%20including%20us%20though%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20an%20African%20country%20representative%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAU%20is%20not%20a%20politically%20cohesive%20unit.%20There%20are%20issues%20that%20countries%20are%20facing%20on%20their%20own%20and%20with%20each%20other.%20Besides%2C%20there%20are%20eight%20regional%20economic%20committees%20which%20have%20developed%20individually%20with%20differing%20structures%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20another%20source%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693817158000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04141303%2FFjHNMmeakAEkbxa.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-likely-to-become-g21-with-induction-of-african-union%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Within%20the%20African%20Union%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20whether%20joining%20the%20G20%20would%20be%20beneficial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2