0itself%20by%20about%2040%20cm%20as%20expected%20and%20landed%20safely%20at%20a%20distance%20of%2030%20%E2%80%93%2040%20cm%20away.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT63t3MVUvI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FT63t3MVUvI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1698570774385205621%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20said%20this%20achievement%20%26quot%3Bkickstart%20enthuses%20future%20sample%20return%20and%20human%20missions.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20said%20that%20Vikram's%20systems%20are%20healthy%20and%20performed%20nominally.%20%26quot%3BVikram's%20systems%20deployed%20ramp%2C%20equipment%20folded%20back%20and%20redeployed%20successfully%20after%20the%20experiment%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission's%20Pragyan%20rover%20was%20%26quot%3Bset%20into%20Sleep%20mode%26quot%3B%20but%20with%20batteries%20charged%20and%20receiver%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHoping%20for%20a%20successful%20awakening%20for%20another%20set%20of%20assignments.%20Else%2C%20it%20will%20forever%20stay%20there%20as%20India's%20lunar%20ambassador%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20space%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20country%20to%20land%20near%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon%20with%20its%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3's%20soft%2C%20textbook%20touchdown%20after%20a%20failed%20attempt%20in%202019%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20jubilation%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0The%20landing%2C%20which%20came%20just%20days%20after%20a%20Russian%20lander%20crashed%20in%20the%20same%20region%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20India's%20greatest%20scientific%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20been%20steadily%20matching%20the%20achievements%20of%20ot