asions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%20-%20the%20worst%20year%20of%20the%20pandemic%20-%20six%20countries%20were%20led%20by%20individuals%20below%20HoS%2FHoG%20rank.%20In%202022%20-%20after%20Russia's%20illegal%20war%20on%20Ukraine%20-%20three%20sent%20teams%20not%20lead%20by%20designated%20HoS%2FHoGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-xi-jinping-meeting-brics-summit-request-from-chinese-side-india-denies-beijing-claims-on-bilateral-meet-4327919%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BRequest%20From%20Chinese%20Side%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Denies%20Beijing's%20Claims%20On%20PM%20Modi-Xi%20Jinping%20Meet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20India%2C%20Italy%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Turkey%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20have%20always%20sent%20a%20head%20of%20state%20to%20a%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20France%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Japan%20and%20South%20Africa%20have%20not%20done%20so%20on%20one%20instance%20each%2C%20which%20Argentina%2C%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%20and%20Russia%20have%20done%20so%20two%20times%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20said%20he%20will%20be%20disappointed%20if%20Mr%20Jinping%20does%20not%20attend%20but%20added%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20going%20to%20get%20to%20see%20him%26quot%3B%2C%20although%20he%20did%20not%20specify%20when%20and%20where.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdisappointed-but-biden-on-reports-that-xi-may-skip-india-g20-summit-4356895%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDisappointed%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Biden%20On%20Reports%20That%20Xi%20May%20Skip%20India%20G20%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20occasion%20too%2C%20Russia%20will%20not%20be%20represented%20b