0the%20G20%20summit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20arrangements%20made%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20cloud%20kitchens%20and%20other%20delivery%20services%20won't%20be%20allowed%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20during%20the%20summit%20period.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20clarify%20that%20grocery%2C%20ATMs%20and%20medical%20stores%20(essential%20services)%2C%20and%20other%20establishments%20will%20remain%20open%2C%20even%20in%20the%20regulated%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20traffic%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%205-star%20hotels%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20that%20some%20heads%20of%20state%20will%20stay%20at%20Maurya%20Sheraton%20hotel%20in%20Saket%2C%20Lodhi%20hotel%20in%20Southwest%20district%20and%20Hyatt%20at%20Ring%20Road.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20are%20out%20of%20NDMC%20area%20and%20will%20function%20normally.%20Only%20on%20some%20occasions%2C%20when%20there%20will%20be%20movement%20of%20dignitaries%2C%20traffic%20will%20be%20regulated%20temporarily.%20Otherwise%2C%20all%20the%20malls%20and%20hotels%20in%20these%20areas%20will%20function%20normally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAerocity%20will%20also%20remain%20open%2C%20except%20for%202-3%20buildings%20where%20movement%20will%20be%20regulated%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20I%20carry%20out%20my%20morning%20routine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yaday%20said%20in%20the%20Facebook%20Live%20session%20that%20movement%20of%20cars%2C%20bicycles%20and%20other%20vehicles%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20in%20the%20controlled%20zone.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20would%20request%20not%20to%20go%20out%20for%20morning%20walks%20during%20the%20summit%20duration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20there%20be%20restrictions%20on%20the%20Outer%20Ring%20Road%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20police%20