bloody%20counter-offensive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A540%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66702244%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66702244.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66702244.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahmedabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Plans%20to%20Demolish%20Iconic%20Sardar%20Patel%20Stadium%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03203111%2FSVP-stadium.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Ahmedabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(AMC)%20is%20planning%20to%20demolish%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20(SVP)%20Stadium%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahmedabadmirror.com%2Fend-of-an-era%2F81863126.html%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAhmedabad%20Mirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoting%20an%20unnamed%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SVP%20stadium%20is%20not%20to%20be%20confused%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fsardar-patel-cricket-stadium-in-ahmedabad-renamed-after-narendra-modi%5C%22%3EAhmedabad%E2%80%99s%20more%20popular%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20formerly%20known%20as%20the%20Sardar%20Patel%20Stadium%20and%20colloquially%20as%20the%20Motera%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesigned%20in%20the%201960s%20by%20architect%20Charles%20Correa%20and%20engineer%20Mahendra%20Raj%2C%20the%20SVP%20stadium%20was%20built%20to%20host%20international%20cricket%20matches%2C%C2%A0but%20began%20to%20host%20domestic%20ones%20after%20what%20is%20today%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20was%20built%20in%201982%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wmf.org%2Fproject%2Fsardar-vallabhbhai-patel-stadium%5C%22%3Ethe%20World%20Monuments%20Fund%20(WMF)%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20Stadium%20%E2%80%A6%20represents%20the%20progressive%20ideals%20and%20experimental%20spirit%20that%20characterised%20India%E2%80%99s%20post-independence%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20New%20York-based%20heritage%20organisation%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20going%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20demolition%20of%20the%20structure.%20Instead%20of%20spending%20crores%20on%20repairing%2C%20construction%20of%20a%20new%20one%20is%20a%20better%20idea%20which%20would%20last%20for%20another%2050-60%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20the%20AMC%20leader%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20AMC%20plans%20to%20replace%20the%2063-year-old%20stadium%20with%20a%20new%2C%20state-of-the-art%20one%20as%20part%20of%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20anticipated%20bid%20for%20the%202036%20Summer%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201982%2C%20the%20stadium%20has%20also%20become%20a%20popular%20space%20for%20recreational%20use%20by%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20residents.%20But%20due%20to%20what%20the%20WMF%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cdecades%20of%20poor%20maintenance%20and%20lack%20of%20funding%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20stadium%20has%20become%20worn%20down%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EMirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20that%20it%20has%20even%20become%20%E2%80%9Chazardous%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20even%20fit%20for%20organizing%20any%20cultural%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20quoted%20an%20AMC%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202020%2C%20the%20arts-focused%20grants%20provider%20Getty%20Foundation%20announced%20a%20grant%20to%20the%20stadium%2C%20following%20which%20the%20WMF%20launched%20a%20project%20along%20with%20the%20AMC%20to%20conserve%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stadium%E2%80%99s%20distinct%2C%20cantilevered%20framing%20takes%20its%20structural%20power%20from%20an%20elegantly%20zig-zagging%20exterior%20wall%20that%20provides%20added%20reinforcement.%20This%20solution%20was%20reached%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Mahendra%20Raj%2C%20a%20pioneering%20engineer%20who%20helped%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20modern%20architects%20turn%20their%20design%20visions%20into%20reality%E2%80%A6%20The%20site%20has%20been%20placed%20on%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wmf.org%2F2020Watch%5C%22%3E2020%20World%20Monuments%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20selection%20of%20at-risk%20cultural%20heritage%20sites%20that%20conjoin%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20historical%20significance%20with%20contemporary%20social%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20the%20Getty%20Foundation%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getty.edu%2Fnews%2Fgetty-announces-final-round-keeping-it-modern-architecture-conservation-grants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Patel%20Stadium%20was%20one%20of%2013%20significant%20twentieth-century%20buildings%20in%20the%20world%20that%20would%20receive%20a%20total%20of%20%242.2%20million%20in%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20interview%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMid-Day%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fsunday-mid-day%2Farticle%2Fsardar-of-stadiums-23276011%5C%22%3EWMF%20had%20handed%20the%20project%20over%20to%20the%20AMC%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20what%20was%20then%20the%20Sardar%20Patel%20Stadium%20was%20renovated%20and%20turned%20into%20becoming%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20stadium%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-australia-narendra-modi-stadium%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20capacity%20to%20host%201.32%20lakh%20spectators%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20was%20renamed%20after%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20SVP%20stadium%2C%20a%20second%20project%20in%20Ahmedabad%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20for%20its%20renovation%20ambitions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Sabarmati%20Ashram%2C%20which%20served%20as%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20home%20from%201917%20to%201930.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Rs%201%2C200-crore%20plan%20to%20refurbish%20the%20ashram%20said%20that%20these%20plans%20aimed%20at%20commercialising%20a%20space%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsabarmati-ashram-world-class-memorial-gandhi-simplicity%5C%22%3Eotherwise%20represents%20the%20simplicity%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20thought%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693756032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03203111%2FSVP-stadium.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famc-plans-to-demolish-sardar-vallabhbhai-patel-stadium-report-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20World%20Monuments%20Fund%20says%20the%20stadium%20%26quot%3Brepresents%20the%20progressive%20ideals%20and%20experimental%20spirit%20that%20characterised%20India%E2%80%99s%20post-independence%20period%26quot%3B.%20In%202020%2C%20it%20was%20listed%20as%20one%20of%2013%20significant%20twentieth-century%20buildings%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famc-plans-to-demolish-sardar-vallabhbhai-patel-stadium-report-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italian%20Grand%20Prix%3A%20Max%20Verstappen%20in%20record-breaking%2010th%20consecutive%20F1%20win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693755667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Flive-experience%2Fcps%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F1065F%2Fproduction%2F_130976176_verstappen_10_getty3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Fformula1%2F66701564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Red%20Bull's%20M