20for%20example%2C%2012%20sites%20that%20are%20prone%20to%20flooding%20and%20dumping%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20urban%20forests%20through%20the%20Kochi%20Municipal%20Corporation%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wri-india.org%2Fblog%2Fkawaki-community-led-tree-based-intervention-climate-resilience-case-study%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKawaki%20initiative.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20erstwhile%20mosquito%20breeding%20grounds%20are%20now%20seeing%20the%20scientific%20plantation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20saplings%2C%20which%20as%20fully%20grown%20trees%20will%20offer%20much%20needed%20heat%20mitigation%20through%20green%20cover%20and%20permeable%20surfaces%20that%20can%20absorb%20rainfall%20and%20help%20recharge%20groundwater.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20municipal%20corporation%2C%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.auegskerala.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAyyankali%20Urban%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(AUEGS)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20trained%20over%20a%20hundred%20workers%20on%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20urban%20forests%20and%20are%20teaching%20them%20how%20to%20prepare%20the%20soil%20for%20sowing%2C%20plant%20saplings%2C%20water%20and%20weed%20the%20area%2C%20and%20build%20low-cost%20tree%20guards%20to%20protect%20the%20saplings%20from%20animals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20implementation%20of%20this%20programme%20in%20her%20own%20neighbourhood%2C%20Sindhu%20Jayan%2C%20a%20worker%20with%20the%20Ayyankali%20Scheme%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20work%20has%20been%20very%20different%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20glad%20to%20have%20learned%20these%20new%20skills.%20The%20deserted%20graveyard%20was%20a%20scary%20and%20unwelcoming%20place%2C%20but%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20turn%20what%20will%20be%20our%20final%20resting%20place%20into%20a%20beautiful%20grove.%E2%80%9D%3C%2F