%2C%20and%20has%20purchased%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302115%2Fdelhi-doctors-and-volunteers-give-free-healthcare-to-poor-people-on-streets-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20land%20in%20Noida%20and%20Ghaziabad%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20easy%20to%20take%20a%20wrong%20turn%20and%20fall%20into%20bad%20company.%20Have%20courage%20to%20move%20ahead%20in%20life.%20From%20being%20hungry%20all%20the%20time%2C%20I%20am%20now%20able%20to%20feed%20many.%20You%20too%20can%20achieve%20your%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lilyma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692698796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Flilyy-1692624383.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lilyma%20Khan%20is%20the%20head%20chef%20at%20Dear%20Donna%20in%20Delhi.%20She%20recalls%20the%20struggle%20she%20faced%20to%20get%20here%2C%20how%20her%20love%20for%20cooking%20came%20to%20be%2C%20and%20how%20she%20forged%20past%20all%20the%20obstacles%20that%20life%20threw%20her%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20Say%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Death%20Sentence%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20I%20Wish%20People%20Knew%20About%20Living%20with%20HIV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Homophobia%2C%20bullying%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20myths%20associated%20with%20HIV%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20death%20sentence.%20%5BBut%5D%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20those%20who%20are%20not%20