%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20other%20teenager%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20and%20why%20it%20was%20happening%20to%20me.%20I%20felt%20alone.%20Back%20in%202008%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20sufficient%20access%20to%20the%20internet.%20Through%20interviews%20on%20television%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20homosexuality.%20I%20contacted%20Prince%20Manvendra%2C%20who%20advised%20me%20to%20connect%20with%20Naz%20Foundation.%20Through%20counselling%2C%20I%20understood%20I%20am%20gay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Gautam%20came%20to%20know%20about%20his%20sexuality.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327817%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Gautam%20discovered%20his%20sexuality.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20these%20sessions%20that%20the%20counsellor%20suggested%20that%20Gautam%20be%20tested%20for%20HIV%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20multiple%20sexual%20partners.%20And%20though%20he%20had%20no%20symptoms%2C%20he%20teste